title: Hour 2 - Aaron Rodgers Gets Psychedelic
itunes:title: Hour 2 - Aaron Rodgers Gets Psychedelic
description:
Today on The Dan Patrick Show, Dan discusses Packers QB Aaron Rodgers and what he's used in the offseason to help him play better on the football field, and it might come from an unlikely source — ayahuasca. Dan and the Danettes discuss if THEY would try the hallucinogens themselves!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
